Name: Material UI
Author: skotlex
Description:
Material UI replaces FFXIV's built-in theme (dark-theme). This mod is the Black version which targets a more modern dark color with an edged UI. Currently this modpack only supports the 4K HUD resoltion settings. If you do not have this enabled at this time, you can change over to by by doing the following:

1. Click ESC key on keyboard → System Configuration → Graphic Settings tab → UI Resolution Settings
2. Choose the option: High (4k)
3. Reset your game.

Please note that if you change any of the mod's configurations you will need to logout and log back in again as redraws will not effect your HUD and System UI.
